text: O vi kred witnessing vol when unu de vi mort done 2 equitable popol vi! Vi vojagx tiam 2 others do des witnessing! Post observ Kontakt Prayer (Salat) let witnesses jxur DI alleviate your dub Ni ne uz this ating personal gajn eben testator est rilat al us! Nor vol ni conceal di testimony. Otherwise ni est sinners
